%% WarpTalk Module 1 - Translation Room Management
%% Recommended Audio Routing State Diagram
%% Converted from PDF to Mermaid

---
title: Recommended Audio Routing State Diagram
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IDLE: START
    IDLE --> ROUTING_READY: config ready
    ROUTING_READY --> AUDIO_ROUTING_ACTIVE: session starts

    AUDIO_ROUTING_ACTIVE --> AUDIO_ROUTING_PAUSED: room pause
    AUDIO_ROUTING_PAUSED --> AUDIO_ROUTING_ACTIVE: room resume

    AUDIO_ROUTING_ACTIVE --> STT_DEGRADED: stt latency high
    STT_DEGRADED --> AUDIO_ROUTING_ACTIVE: stt recovered

    AUDIO_ROUTING_ACTIVE --> TRANSLATION_DEGRADED: translation latency high
    TRANSLATION_DEGRADED --> AUDIO_ROUTING_ACTIVE: translation recovered

    AUDIO_ROUTING_ACTIVE --> TTS_DEGRADED: tts latency high
    TTS_DEGRADED --> AUDIO_ROUTING_ACTIVE: tts recovered

    AUDIO_ROUTING_ACTIVE --> VOICE_CLONE_FALLBACK: voice clone unavailable
    VOICE_CLONE_FALLBACK --> AUDIO_ROUTING_ACTIVE: voice clone recovered

    AUDIO_ROUTING_ACTIVE --> TEXT_ONLY_MODE: audio unavailable
    TTS_DEGRADED --> TEXT_ONLY_MODE: tts unavailable
    VOICE_CLONE_FALLBACK --> TEXT_ONLY_MODE: tts unavailable
    TEXT_ONLY_MODE --> AUDIO_ROUTING_ACTIVE: audio recovered

    AUDIO_ROUTING_ACTIVE --> STOPPING: session ends or system disables
    AUDIO_ROUTING_PAUSED --> STOPPING: session ends or system disables
    STT_DEGRADED --> STOPPING: session ends or system disables
    TRANSLATION_DEGRADED --> STOPPING: session ends or system disables
    TTS_DEGRADED --> STOPPING: session ends or system disables
    VOICE_CLONE_FALLBACK --> STOPPING: session ends or system disables
    TEXT_ONLY_MODE --> STOPPING: session ends or system disables

    STOPPING --> FINALIZING_ARTIFACTS: flush runtime
    FINALIZING_ARTIFACTS --> COMPLETED: outputs linked
    COMPLETED --> [*]: END
